# Preview after edits

When you finish changes to this static site (HTML, CSS, JS, or assets used by the home page), open the home page in the default browser so the user can preview immediately.

From the project root, run:

```bash
open index.html
```

(On macOS this uses the default browser. If the command fails, use the full path to `index.html` in the workspace.)

Do this **once** at the end of a task after saving files—not after every tiny single-line edit in a multi-step session.
